    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll start drafting that. one thing tho—since you've been handling all the personalized itineraries for the high-net-worth clients, i'm a bit worried the new engine might not catch all the subtle preferences you've learned over time. i don't want them feeling like the service is getting \"robotic\" or losing that luxury touch. do you think the new model will actually be able to keep up with the level of nuance you provide?",
